text: Latest #CARecall ballot tracker from @paulmitche11 shows 1.5m votes cast so far (7%), and Democrats widening their lead slightly in sending those ballots back. 57% have come from Dems, 22% indie, 21% GOP. Mostly from older, white voters. Dems well ahead of 2020 early voting pace. https://t.co/4p7MT9E3yM
